<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利越长越大，不断学习森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一年，干旱非常严重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当几乎不下雨的冬天到来时，开始干旱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山药干巴巴的，树几乎没开花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，天慢慢热了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酷热使森林变成了黄色、褐色，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后变成了黑色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水坑变成了淤泥。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>竹子枝条干枯，被热风吹得沙沙响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利第一次觉得饿极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>饥饿很可怕，口渴更严重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酷热持续着，晒干了所有的水分。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，只有一条河里有水了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈提，智慧的老象，举起了他的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“水中停战！”他宣布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利学过，那是没人可以在水里打猎的意思。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，所有人都可以安全地在那里喝水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>动物们吹着口哨尖叫，把 “水中停战”的消息传了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这段时间太可怕了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，巴希拉在河边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>空气感觉像火一样热。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁叹了口气。“今年雨忘记了我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在上游，哈提和他的儿子们站在月光下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>附近有几只鹿、猪和野牛在喝水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类也很饿。”一头猪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们死在他们的田里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈提，你见过这么严重的干旱吗？”巴鲁问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，但这干旱会过去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈提往自己的后背和侧腰喷了喷水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁看着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我们这里有个人再没食物就活不下去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个男孩儿已经皮包骨了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！”毛克利从水里坐起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是因为我没有毛覆盖身体。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，毛克利瞪着巴鲁说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没有毛也会看起来不好看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉抬起一只爪子轻轻地把毛克利推到了水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利站起来，边吐水边大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这样逗你老师，太没礼貌了，毛克利。”巴希拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他扑哧一笑，又把毛克利推到了水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次当毛克利从水里站起来时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见巴希拉的表情变了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃哦。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见老虎在朝他们慢慢走过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，看啊。”谢尔坎声音低沉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他俯身要喝水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是那个人类孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利悄悄退到巴希拉身后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎把下巴放进河里喝水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，河面上就泛起了油乎乎的水纹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉怀疑地看着那些油乎乎的水纹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎，你做了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎阴险地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我发现了一个人类。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我才来河里喝水，清洗一下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几只动物吓得倒吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在干旱时期杀了一个人？”巴希拉厉声问道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“找不到别的吃的了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎只是耸了耸肩膀，什么也没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈提静静地听着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他走近谢尔坎，摆动他的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道，谢尔坎，现在是干旱时期。”大象说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“河水是给大家喝的，不是洗血迹的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，我们都在遭受折磨，包括森林动物和人类。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在炫耀杀人是不对的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你喝够水了吗？”哈提问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就走吧！”哈提命令说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的三个儿子站到了他的身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎一声不吭就走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他知道大家都知道的一个事实——哈提是森林的主人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉叹了口气，转身对毛克利说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>369784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“永远不要忘记这个，小兄弟，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>369784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>375420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎是你的敌人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>